cs.AR, cs.ET, cs.NE, cs.DC, cs.SY

This paper deals with the resilience of Deep Neural Networks (DNNs) in the presence of voltage underscaling related faults of FPGAs. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) as it deals with the design and analysis of hardware systems. The paper also discusses the use of FPGAs for DNNs, which falls under cs.ET (Embedded Systems) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also evaluates the resilience of DNNs, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
